                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-blue-700">ບົດຮຽນພາສາອັງກິດ</h2>

                <!-- Module 1: Basic Vocabulary -->
                <div class="mb-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="module-header bg-gray-100 p-4 flex justify-between items-center" onclick="toggleModule('module1')">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700">1. ຄຳສັບພື້ນຖານ (Basic Vocabulary)</h3>
                        <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-500">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="module1-content" class="module-content p-4 border-t border-gray-200 hidden">
                        <p class="mb-2">ຮຽນຮູ້ຄຳສັບທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນຊີວິດປະຈຳວັນເຊັ່ນ: Good morning, Hello, Thank you, Please, Excuse me.</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600">
                            <li>Hello! (ສະບາຍດີ!)</li>
                            <li>Good morning! (ສະບາຍດີຕອນເຊົ້າ!)</li>
                            <li>Thank you! (ຂອບໃຈ!)</li>
                            <li>Please (ກະລຸນາ)</li>
                            <li>Excuse me (ຂໍໂທດ / ອະນຸຍາດ)</li>
                            <li>Yes / No (ແມ່ນ / ບໍ່)</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">ທ່ານສາມາດຄລິກທີ່ຫົວຂໍ້ເພື່ອປິດ/ເປີດບົດຮຽນ.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Module 2: Grammar Basics -->
                <div class="mb-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="module-header bg-gray-100 p-4 flex justify-between items-center" onclick="toggleModule('module2')">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700">2. ໄວຍາກອນ (Grammar)</h3>
                        <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-500">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="module2-content" class="module-content p-4 border-t border-gray-200 hidden">
                        <p class="mb-2">ເຂົ້າໃຈໂຄງສ້າງປະໂຫຍກພື້ນຖານ: Subject + Verb + Object. (ປະທານ + ຄຳກຳມະ + ກຳ). ຕົວຢ່າງ:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600">
                            <li>I eat rice. (ຂ້ອຍກິນເຂົ້າ.)</li>
                            <li>You like coffee. (ເຈົ້າມັກກາເຟ.)</li>
                            <li>She studies English. (ລາວຜູ້ຍິງຮຽນພາສາອັງກິດ.)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Module 3: Pronunciation -->
                <div class="mb-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="module-header bg-gray-100 p-4 flex justify-between items-center" onclick="toggleModule('module3')">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700">3. ການອອກສຽງ (Pronunciation)</h3>
                        <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-500">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="module3-content" class="module-content p-4 border-t border-gray-200 hidden">
                        <p class="mb-2">ຝຶກອອກສຽງພະຍັນຊະນະ ແລະ ສະຫຼະທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນໃນພາສາອັງກິດ. ຄວາມສຳຄັນຂອງການອອກສຽງທີ່ຊັດເຈນ.</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600">
                            <li>"th" sound (e.g., "thank," "this")</li>
                            <li>Vowel sounds (long/short vowels)</li>
                            <li>Stress in words and sentences</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Module 4: Daily Conversation -->
                <div class="mb-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="module-header bg-gray-100 p-4 flex justify-between items-center" onclick="toggleModule('module4')">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700">4. ການສົນທະນາປະຈຳວັນ (Daily Conversation)</h3>
                        <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-500">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="module4-content" class="module-content p-4 border-t border-gray-200 hidden">
                        <p class="mb-2">ປະໂຫຍກທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນການທັກທາຍ, ແນະນຳຕົວ, ສັ່ງອາຫານ, ແລະ ອື່ນໆ.</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600">
                            <li>"How are you?" (ທ່ານສະບາຍດີບໍ?)</li>
                            <li>"What is your name?" (ເຈົ້າຊື່ຫຍັງ?)</li>
                            <li>"Can I have a coffee, please?" (ຂໍກາເຟແດ່, ກະລຸນາ)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </section>

            <!-- Interactive Quiz Section -->
            <aside class="lg:col-span-1 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-blue-700">ແບບທົດສອບຄວາມຮູ້</h2>

                <div id="quiz-area" class="text-left">
                    <p id="quiz-question" class="text-lg font-medium mb-4 text-gray-700">ກົດ "ເລີ່ມທົດສອບ" ເພື່ອເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ.</p>
                    <div id="quiz-options" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 mb-4">
                        <!-- Quiz options will be loaded here by JS -->
                    </div>
                    <div id="quiz-feedback" class="feedback-box text-center font-semibold text-sm rounded-lg py-2 mb-4 hidden"></div>

                    <button id="start-quiz-btn" class="w-full bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg">ເລີ່ມທົດສອບ</button>
                    <button id="next-question-btn" class="w-full bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg mt-3 hidden">ຄຳຖາມຕໍ່ໄປ</button>
                    <button id="retake-quiz-btn" class="w-full bg-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg mt-3 hidden">ທົດສອບອີກຄັ້ງ</button>
                </div>
